Data Structures
Here are the data structures with brief descriptions:
 CDmaEvtListThe structure which holds the rx/tx event numbers. The event number 'FFFF' is invalid
 CHWConfigDataSPI Hardware Configuartion Structure
 CMcspi_ChanParamsStructure to get the user param to enable the cross bar interrupt on M3 core
 CMcspi_ConfigChfmtStructure to initialize the SPI transfer format register
 CMcspi_DataParamData packet element structure passed to submit function
 CMcspi_FifoTrigLvlStructure to set the rx/tx trigger level using the IOCTL
 CMcspi_ParamsMcspi Instance configuration parameters
 CpwrmInfoStructure for holding the PWRM related info
 CStatsMcSPI statistics Collection Object
